                        <additions>
                            <list>
                                <item xml:id="a1">
                                    <desc type="Inventory"/>
                                    <locus target="#248"/>
                                    <q xml:lang="gez">
                                        ኍልቈ፡ መጻሕፍት፡ ዘቤተ፡ ክርስቲያን። ፪ትርጓሜ፡ ጰውሎስ። ፩ትርጓሜ፡ ዕብራውያን። ፩ውዳሴ፡ አምላክ፡ ምስለ፡ ዮሐንስ፡ ወንጌል። ፩ገድለ፡ ሐዋርያት። ፩ገድለ፡ ጴጥሮስ። ፩ኦርጋኖን። ፩ትርጓሜ፡ 
                                        ደዊት። ፩መጽሐፈ፡ መድኃኒት፡ ምስለ፡ በአውልት። ፩ድጓ። ፪ዝማሬ። ፩ትርጓሜ፡ ደቂቀ፡ ነቢያት። ፩አፈ፡ ወርቅ። ዮሐንስ፡ ወንጌል፡ ምስለ፡ ቀለምሲስ። ሲኖዶስ። ፩አረጋዊ፡ ጰውሎስ። ፩ዜና፡ 
                                        አይሁድ። ፩ዜና፡ አበው፡ ዘበልዕዎ፡ አናጹት። ወኵሉ፡ ድሙር፡ ፲ወ፱፡ ፩ኪዳን፡ ዘምስለ፡ መዝገበ፡ መልክዕ፡ ወስብሐተ፡ ፍቁር፡ ወሰዓታት፡ ዘመአልት፡ ገድለ፡ ገብረ፡ መንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ። ፩አረቢ።
                                    </q>
                                    <desc>The inventory lists the books belonging to the church: two <ref type="work" corresp="LIT3181Commen">Tǝrgʷāme Ṗāwlos</ref>, 
                                        one <ref type="work" corresp="LIT3171Commen">Tǝrgʷāme ʿƎbrāwǝyān</ref>, 
                                        one <ref type="work" corresp="LIT2505Weddas">Wǝddāse ʾAmlāk</ref> with the <ref type="work" corresp="LIT1693John">Gospel of John</ref>, 
                                        one <ref type="work" corresp="LIT1461Gadlah">Gadla ḥawāryāt</ref>, one <foreign xml:lang="gez">Gadla Ṗeṭros</foreign>, one 
                                        <ref type="work" corresp="LIT1146Argano">ʾArgānona Māryām</ref>, 
                                        one <ref type="work" corresp="LIT3182Commen">Tǝrgʷāme Dāwit</ref>, one <ref type="work" corresp="LIT1942Mashaf">Maṣḥafa madḫanit</ref> with commemorations, 
                                        one <ref type="work" corresp="LIT3178Deggwa">Dǝggʷā</ref>, two <ref type="work" corresp="LIT2610Zemmar">Zǝmmāre</ref>, one <ref type="work" corresp="LIT3183Commen">Tǝrgʷāme daqiqa nabiyāt</ref>, 
                                        one <ref type="work" corresp="LIT3184Afawarq">ʾAfa Warq</ref>, <ref type="work" corresp="LIT1693John">Gospel of John</ref> with the 
                                        <ref type="work" corresp="LIT3179Revela">Revelation</ref>, one <ref type="work" corresp="LIT2317Senodo">Sinodos</ref>, one ʾAragāwi Ṗawlos (presumably 
                                        the <ref type="work" corresp="LIT1803Lifeof">Life of Paul the First Hermit</ref> ), one <ref type="work" corresp="LIT2598Yosipp">Zenā ʾAyhud</ref>, 
                                        one <ref type="work" corresp="LIT2611Zenaab">Zenā ʾabaw</ref>. 
                                        The total amount of the previous books is 19. Additionally, one <foreign xml:lang="gez">Kidān</foreign> with the <ref type="work" corresp="LIT3185Mazgab">Mazgaba malkǝʾ</ref>, 
                                        the <ref type="work" corresp="LIT2300Sebhat">Sǝbḥata fǝqur</ref> and the <ref type="work" corresp="LIT2231Saatat">Saʿātāt za-maʿālt</ref>, 
                                        one <ref type="work" corresp="LIT1451GadlaG">Gadla Gabra Manfas Qǝddus</ref>, one in Arabic.</desc>
                                </item>
                                
                                <item xml:id="a2">
                                    <desc type="Inventory"/>
                                    <locus target="#248"/>
                                    <q xml:lang="gez">
                                        ዘሀለወ፡ ለአባ፡ ተስፋ፡ ወንጌል፡ ዮሐንስ፡ ምስለ፡ ቀለምሲስ፡ ፩ደዊት፡ የአባ፡ ስጦት፡ በቄስባይነሶ፡ ፩ድጓ፡ ፩ዝማሬ፡ ምስለ፡ ምዕራፍ፡ ወመዋሥዕት፡ ወቃለ፡ ትምህርት፡ ወውዳሴ፡ ማርያም፡ ፲ወ፬ቅዳሴ፡ 
                                        ወሊጦን፡ ወዘይነግሥ፡ <gap reason="omitted" extent="unknown"/> ፩ዜና፡ ስላሴ።
                                    </q>
                                    <desc>The inventory is partly written in Amharic, in a different hand than that of <ref target="#a1"/>. 
                                        It lists the books belonging to  
                                        <persName ref="PRS10796Tasfo">
                                 <roleName type="title">ʾabbā</roleName> Tasfo</persName>, i.e. the <ref type="work" corresp="LIT1693John">Gospel of John</ref> 
                                        with the <ref type="work" corresp="LIT3179Revela">Revelation</ref> and the <ref type="work" corresp="LIT2701Dawit">Dāwit</ref>, 
                                        and those belonging to  
                                        <persName ref="PRS10797Setot">
                                 <roleName type="title">ʾabbā</roleName> Sǝṭot</persName>,  i.e. one <ref type="work" corresp="LIT3178Deggwa">Dǝggʷā</ref>, 
                                        one <ref type="work" corresp="LIT2610Zemmar">Zǝmmāre</ref> with the <ref type="work" corresp="LIT3186Meeraf">Mǝʿrāf</ref> 
                                        and the <ref type="work" corresp="LIT1990Mawase">Mawāśǝʾǝt</ref>, 
                                        the <ref type="work" corresp="LIT3187Qalatem">Qāla tǝmhǝrt</ref>, the <ref type="work" corresp="LIT2509Weddas">Wǝddāse Māryām</ref>, 
                                            the <ref type="work" corresp="LIT3189Anapho">fourteen Anaphoras</ref>, the <ref type="work" corresp="LIT3188Liton">Liṭon</ref>, 
                                            the <ref type="work" corresp="LIT2605Zayena">Za-yǝnaggǝś</ref>, one <ref type="work" corresp="LIT1300Dersan">Zenā Śǝllāse</ref>
                                    </desc>
                                </item>
                                
                                <item xml:id="a3">
                                    <desc type="Inventory"/>
                                    <locus target="#248"/>
                                    <q xml:lang="gez">
                                        እምእሉ፡ ዘበጽሐኒ፡ ሊተ፡ ዘማርያም። ትርጓሜ፡ ዕብራውያን። ገድለ፡ ሐዋርያት። ገድለ፡ ጴጥሮስ። መጽሐፈ፡ መድኀኒት። ድጓ። ፪ዝማሬ። አረጋዊ፡ ጰውሎስ። ዜና፡ ሥላሴ። ሰዓታት፡ ዘመዓልት። 
                                        ገድለ፡ ገብረ፡ መንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ። ትርጓሜ፡ ጰውሎስ።
                                    </q>
                                    <desc>The inventory is written in the same hand as that of <ref target="#a2"/>. It lists the books received by the author of the note, 
                                        called <persName ref="PRS10798Zamaryam"/>. 
                                        The books are: the <ref type="work" corresp="LIT3171Commen">Tǝrgʷāme ʿƎbrāwǝyān</ref>, the <ref type="work" corresp="LIT1461Gadlah">Gadla ḥawāryāt</ref>, 
                                        the Gadla Ṗeṭros, the <ref type="work" corresp="LIT1942Mashaf">Maṣḥafa madḫanit</ref>, 
                                        the <ref type="work" corresp="LIT3178Deggwa">Dǝggʷā</ref>, two <ref type="work" corresp="LIT2610Zemmar">Zǝmmāre</ref>, one ʾAragāwi Ṗawlos 
                                        (presumably the <ref type="work" corresp="LIT1803Lifeof">Life of Paul the First Hermit</ref> ), 
                                        the <ref type="work" corresp="LIT2611Zenaab">Zenā ʾabaw</ref>, the <ref type="work" corresp="LIT1300Dersan">Zenā Śǝllāse</ref>, the 
                                        <ref type="work" corresp="LIT2231Saatat">Saʿātāt za-maʿālt</ref>, the <ref type="work" corresp="LIT1451GadlaG">Gadla Gabra Manfas Qǝddus</ref>, 
                                        <ref type="work" corresp="LIT3181Commen">Tǝrgʷāme Ṗāwlos</ref>.</desc>
                                </item>
                                
                            </list>
